1
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:16,640
Come on.

2
00:00:16,839 --> 00:00:17,359
Hurry in.

3
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:19,879
Put them here.

4
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:20,719
Put them here.

5
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:25,239
Put those over there.

6
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:30,399
This is...

7
00:00:33,479 --> 00:00:34,520
The Women's clinic

8
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:36,119
has been gaining popularity in Chang'an.

9
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,399
I'm the boss after all.

10
00:00:37,479 --> 00:00:38,000
Mr. Xiao

11
00:00:38,359 --> 00:00:39,799
is afraid that the clinic can't meet the demand

12
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:40,679
the medicine supply can't keep up,

13
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:41,719
which will affect the reputation.

14
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:44,039
I've brought medicine from the south overnight,

15
00:00:44,439 --> 00:00:45,439
and even calculated the wages.

16
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,479
Mr. Xiao,

17
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,119
you're very considerate.

18
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,240
Xinyue is fortunate

19
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:55,679
to have someone so thoughtful looking out for her.

20
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,000
A'Nong is right.

21
00:00:59,439 --> 00:01:00,320
The medicine issue

22
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:01,359
can't be taken lightly.

23
00:01:02,119 --> 00:01:03,240
I'll go to the backyard.

24
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:06,959
The backyard is over there.

25
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:12,480
Well...

26
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,079
I...

27
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:16,879
I'm sorry.

28
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,719
Five pence a jar.

29
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:27,200
Well...

30
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,400
It's hard to do business.

31
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,640
In the past few months,

32
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,400
we have sold less than 20 boxes

33
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:36,120
of ointment.

34
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,480
Our regular customers

35
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,040
are all flocking to that Women's clinic

36
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,760
to buy some Warm Palace Ointment.

37
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,280
At five pence a jar,

38
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,480
it's half the price

39
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,599
of ours.

40
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,840
If this continues,

41
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,480
we'll be out of business!

42
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,599
Exactly!

43
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,519
I heard

44
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,040
the owner of Ren'an Hall mentioned

45
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,359
the Xiao family's master

46
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:54,400
sent three carts of medicine from the south overnight.

47
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,120
Even our monopoly on Minshan angelica

48
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,159
has been taken by them.

49
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:57,799
If this continues,

50
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,319
we won't even be able to do the medicine business.

51
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,000
I've said it before,

52
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,719
that Women's Clinic hasn't been verified by the guild.

53
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,799
Who knows what's in

54
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,319
their Warm Palace Ointment?

55
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,560
I and you...

56
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,159
Shut up!

57
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,759
What's the point of arguing?

58
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,159
We need a solution.

59
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,199
How about hiring some thugs

60
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:19,400
to hang around the clinic every day,

61
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,680
saying that

62
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,000
women shouldn't be practicing medicine,

63
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:24,319
it's improper.

64
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,639
That way, those noble ladies

65
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:26,639
will be too embarrassed to go there.

66
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:27,800
Good.

67
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,400
Not good.

68
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,879
The Women's clinic

69
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:30,960
is backed by the Xiao Family.

70
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,520
It's not wise to confront them openly.

71
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:34,919
No matter how powerful the Xiao Family is,

72
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,800
they can't defy the law.

73
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:39,560
The Warm Palace Ointment is unapproved,

74
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,199
and sold illegally.

75
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,439
That's already against the law.

76
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,599
Tomorrow,

77
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:45,520
I'll file a complaint at the court.

78
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,319
I'll claim she's selling fake medicine,

79
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,360
causing harm.

80
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:49,280
One death

81
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,639
is enough to warrant her execution.

82
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,039
Master,

83
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,240
but her medicine

84
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,400
is effective.

85
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,039
Effective?

86
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,919
The people are easily misled,

87
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,840
and the truth is hard to reveal.

88
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:03,280
As long as we muddy the waters,

89
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,960
she won't be able to stand.

90
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,439
Let's do it this way.

91
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,479
I'll go find a few trustworthy people.

92
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,960
I'll make sure that the Women's Clinic

93
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,560
is closed.

94
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,560
Slow down.

95
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:15,759
Yan Ge.

96
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:16,960
There are many people today.

97
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,479
come down and help Xinyue with triage.

98
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,000
Take this number

99
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,800
and go queue over there.

100
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:29,879
Next one.

101
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,520
One for the female surgery.

102
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,800
Quack doctor!

103
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,080
Women practicing medicine

104
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,680
violates the natural order.

105
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,560
Now they're getting their just desserts!

106
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,879
How long has this been going on?

107
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,759
Quack doctor!

108
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,319
Quack doctor, come out!

109
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,240
You killed her!

110
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:58,680
Quack doctor, come out!

111
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,080
You killed her!

112
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,919
The Women's clinic killed her!

113
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,360
She's a fraud!

114
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,400
My daughter

115
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,960
took the medicine she prescribed,

116
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,080
and suffered from unbearable pain

117
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,400
for days!

118
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:11,599
Today,

119
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:12,360
today,

120
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,680
she just passed away like this.

121
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,360
The so-called female medicine master

122
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,879
actually killed someone.

123
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,600
Are you still going to let her

124
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,800
continue treating patients?

125
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,800
She has tarnished the reputation of physicians,

126
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,959
a disgrace to the medical community.

127
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:25,759
Today,

128
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:27,279
if you don't give us an explanation,

129
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:29,199
I'll cover the front with paper money.

130
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,920
Let's see how long

131
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,319
this clinic can stay open!

132
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,360
It's you!

133
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,600
You killed my sister!

134
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:35,560
Pay back with your life!

135
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:35,879
Stop!

136
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,120
If the clinic harms people,

137
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,199
the law will deal with it.

138
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,920
You can't take the law into your own hands!

139
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:41,879
You...

140
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,319
What do you have to say?

141
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:45,680
Carrying corpses to protest,

142
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,360
and scattering paper money on the road,

143
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:50,160
do you dare let me examine them publicly?

144
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:51,879
Sir,

145
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,079
arrest her!

146
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,720
She must not harm anyone else!

147
00:04:59,279 --> 00:04:59,879
Mr. Xiao,

148
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:01,439
are you going to protect

149
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,639
this murderer?

150
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,759
Sir, may I take a closer look?

151
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,160
She's probably trying to tamper

152
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,279
with the body,

153
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,560
cover up the evidence!

154
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,120
Without examining the body,

155
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,319
how can you blame the Women's Clinic?

156
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,000
What if it was a chronic illness

157
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,040
or there's another hidden truth?

158
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:22,040
You can't just convict us like this!

159
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:53,920
The corpse is rising!

160
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,399
She made the corpse rise!

161
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,920
How is this possible?

162
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,319
How could this fake death technique

163
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,680
be exposed?

164
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,120
It's broad daylight.

165
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,040
What are you afraid of?

166
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,439
You...

167
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,639
How dare you be so malicious

168
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,480
and show disrespect to the deceased?

169
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,160
I...

170
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,560
Are you so sure your sister is dead?

171
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,600
How about

172
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,720
I bring her back to life?

173
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,199
You...

174
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,560
What did you say?

175
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:24,639
Look!

176
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,480
What are you doing?

177
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,279
I don't know.

178
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:39,439
It's fire therapy.

179
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,920
Here we go.

180
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,959
You can't even tell the difference between wine and water.

181
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,560
Good.

182
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,399
So, you two are the liars.

183
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,319
No, no, no.

184
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:01,759
No.

185
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,439
No, no.

186
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,639
It's not my fault.

187
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:06,160
I'm just the head of the Medical Guild.

188
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,199
I'm just upholding justice.

189
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:07,879
Take them away.

190
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:09,959
Let me go.

191
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,639
What are you doing?

192
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,319
Please wait, Guild Master.

193
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,160
What?

194
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,680
Are you trying to implicate me in this?

195
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:16,839
Do you have any evidence?

196
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,639
Master,

197
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,120
my Women's Clinic

198
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,240
has been open for many months,

199
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:25,639
but we have never visited the guild.

200
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,120
We apologize for the lack of manners.

201
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,959
We will visit another day.

202
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,879
We would appreciate

203
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,319
your guidance.

204
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,279
Xuezhi.

205
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,160
Come.

206
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,000
I've heard that a new

207
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,360
Women's clinic has opened in Chang'an,

208
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,000
and it's very popular with the ladies.

209
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,399
This is Madam Yin,

210
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,680
and this is Madam Su.

211
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,040
Xuezhi

212
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,959
is my best friend from the Bright Moon Pavilion.

213
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,600
We grew up together since childhood.

214
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,920
You're pregnant?

215
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,559
Yes.

216
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,559
Yan Ge,

217
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,279
I came to tell you

218
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,600
that I'm pregnant

219
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,000
and about to leave Chang'an.

220
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,240
What?

221
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,240
What did you say?

222
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,759
It's been two months.

223
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,440
It's from a patron at the Moonlight Pavilion.

224
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:53,960
Are you crazy?

225
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,559
Don't get me wrong.

226
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:59,360
He's different from the other men here.

227
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:01,519
He likes to talk to me

228
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:02,320
about poetry,

229
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,200
the world,

230
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,799
and never treats me with disrespect.

231
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,600
Do you know who you are?

232
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,279
Do you know what would happen

233
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:10,960
if Mom finds out?

234
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,039
You must get rid of this child.

235
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,919
How can you say that?

236
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,919
Do you also think

237
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,399
I'm not worthy of a good man?

238
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:32,960
I'm just worried about your safety.

239
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:38,039
How much do you know about this man?

240
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,399
His surname is Cui.

241
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,879
He's a scholar.

242
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,480
His family owns land.

243
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,679
He's not a playboy.

244
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,440
And he promised me

245
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,279
to marry me

246
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,519
as his wife.

247
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,000
If he truly wishes to marry you,

248
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,720
why hasn't he acted sooner?

249
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,360
The Bright Moon Pavilion is not easily dealt with.

250
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,039
How would your mother allow you to leave with a child?

251
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,279
No,

252
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:11,639
this child

253
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:13,840
must be aborted today.

254
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,639
Yan Ge's concerns are valid.

255
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:21,720
The child you carry is indeed precious,

256
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:22,960
but

257
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,879
the road ahead is perilous and uncertain.

258
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,440
If things go wrong,

259
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,600
your life will be at risk.

260
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,480
I know the road ahead is perilous,

261
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:33,039
but he has promised me a legitimate place.

262
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,519
How can I be trapped in this

263
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:35,639
infernal pit for a lifetime?

264
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:38,480
I had hoped to share this good news with you,

265
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,159
and that you would offer me your blessings.

266
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,480
I apologize for disturbing you.

267
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,600
Today,

268
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:47,440
just pretend I was never here.

269
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,240
Xuezhi!

270
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:54,320
Xuezhi!

271
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:07,279
Yan Ge,

272
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,559
I understand

273
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:12,120
your relationship.

274
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,840
You want to warn her,

275
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,039
but whether she believes

276
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:17,279
his promise or not,

277
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,679
whether she

278
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,200
keeps or discards the child,

279
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,879
these are her choices.

280
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,679
No one can make the decision for her.

281
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:26,360
As her friend,

282
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,480
all you can do

283
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,039
is to stand behind her

284
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,559
and help her

285
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:32,480
when she is hurt.

286
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:44,759
I've been waiting for six hours.

287
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:47,000
He probably never intended to see me.

288
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,639
I can't just keep waiting like this.

289
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:53,639
Still waiting?

290
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,799
The guild's been tied up with trivial matters.

291
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,279
Sorry for the delay.

292
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,399
Forgive me for the disturbance.

293
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:05,639
I came today

294
